claim.claim-text:
1. A reaction apparatus comprising:
a capillary having an inner surface to which a probe molecule that specifically binds to an analyte is immobilized;
a columnar magnetic body that is disposed in a fluid containing the analyte in the capillary;
end-fixing means for fixing one end of the columnar magnetic body in the capillary using a DC magnetic field; and
end-moving means for moving the unfixed end of the columnar magnetic body using an AC magnetic field so as to transfer the fluid forward along the length of the capillary.
